s, Luxe Gift Card, or The Postcard Hotels & Resorts']::text[], 'Global Lounge Collection', 'https://www.americanexpress.com/en-in/charge-cards/apply/personal/platinum', 'https://www.americanexpress.com/content/dam/amex/in/legal/mitc/charge-english-mitc.pdf', 'Section (a)(ii) Annual Membership Fee table, American Express® Platinum Card row: ''First Year Fee: ₹66,000 Second Year onwards ₹66,000''', '2026-06-26', 'needs_review', 'matched', false, now())
