h Care & Grocery, 2x on Utility (bill payments), 1x on other categories','Complimentary domestic lounge access – spend ₹40,000+ in a quarter to get 2 domestic lounge visits the next quarter','Amazon Pay e-Voucher worth ₹400 on minimum spend of ₹5,000 in first 30 days']::text[], 'Lifetime free family lifestyle card', 'https://creditcards.federalbank.co.in', 'https://www.federal.bank.in/credit-cards-mitc', 'SCHEDULE OF CHARGES/TAXES table, Joining Fee / Annual Membership fee rows, Imperio column', '2026-06-26', 'needs_review', 'matched', false, now())
